title: "The Nostalgic Undertow: The Inevitability of Memory Obsolescence in Non-Stationary Environments"
abstract: "Open-access materials accompanying the article «The Nostalgic Undertow: The Inevitability of Memory Obsolescence in Non-Stationary Environments»: manuscript (Russian primary, English translation), supplementary material with the full proofs, bibliography, figures, and self-contained reproducible numerical experiments (Ornstein-Uhlenbeck tracking, fractional-OU and piecewise-stationary-Poisson nostalgia floors, super-linear-memory phase boundary, and a non-circular test of the nostalgia plateau at the tracking floor). Third in the series on the Landauer efficiency of memory, after «Landauer Efficiency of Self-Modeling: An Operational Scale of Vitality» and «The Non-Stationary Landauer Efficiency: Memory Growth, Informational Nostalgia, and the Thermodynamics of Learning Systems»."
